title: Zack Zarrillo from PropertyofZack.com

description:
You have heard me talk about the site forever now get to know the man behind the vision, Zack Zarrillo. He is the owner of Propertyofzack.com and I was able to catch up with him one afternoon and we discussed accidental starts, being raised in Manhattan and tabloid culture.
